  "description": "FUTA spec Example E — credit reduction state with 0.3% reduction. Effective FUTA rate climbs to 0.9%; $2,500 biweekly × 0.009 = $22.50. Verifies the credit-reduction percent flows from employer_config into the calc.",
  "source": "docs/payroll-semantics/futa.md, Worked Example E",
